{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给黄炎培的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给黄炎培的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年8月5日）任之先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大示诵悉。麦去看蒋？，似乎是替台湾起些壮胆作用，别的似乎还谈不到。但我们的准备是必要的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此复，顺致敬意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月五日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]黄炎培，字任之，中国民主建国会主要负责人。当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]指驻日盟军最高司令麦克阿瑟1950年7月31日由日本飞抵台湾，同蒋介石会商如何阻止中国人民解放军解放台湾。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":8,"day":5}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":68,"page_end":68},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}